====================
Soldash Changelog
====================

Version 0.4 - October 17th 2012
----------------------------------------
* Dropped EJS. Now everything is rendered server-side
* Show replication progress
* Better filelist display

Version 0.3 - February 16th 2012
----------------------------------------
* Bugfix release

Version 0.2.1 - December 13th 2011
----------------------------------------
* Fixes for multicore setups

Version 0.2 - December 12th 2011
----------------------------------------
* Version of Solr daemon now displayed
* New On/Off switches

Version 0.1 - November 11th 2011
----------------------------------------

* Core functionality: overview of Solr instances, status, index version
* Out-out-date index highlighting
* Core actions: Fetch Index, Enable/Disable Polling and Replication, Get Filelist, Reload.